{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by the classics of horror gaming, The Tunnels of Saint Mercy Road is a blend of psychological horror, atmospheric horror and creature horror that is certain to give you chills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003530/extras/Description-About.png?t=1729648045\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The tunnels under Saint Mercy road are known for many things. Paranormal encounters... Mysterious cults... Monsters galore... The legends around town spread like a game of telephone. They can't all be true... can they?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>What if I told you that the truth can be revealed, but it would be a journey you have to take... <strong>ALONE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Tunnels of Saint Mercy Road is an immersive horror experience that spans 8 unique areas, each providing a sense of unease and a new mystery to unravel.  Armed with only a lantern, you will descend into the tunnels under Saint Mercy road and explore it's depths and find clues to uncover the truth behind the local legends.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have the courage to descend into darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>I. Dare. You.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003530/extras/Description-Features.png?t=1729648045\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An immersive, single player atmospheric experience (headphones suggested).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 unique areas that will give you a different sense of dread the further you delve. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles and complete objectives to descend further into the dark tunnels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stylized graphics - Re-experience classic horror with a modern first person take.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Short Story - Can be completed in under two hours. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by classic horror games and literature.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamepad Support - Play with your gamepad, keyboard and mouse or accessibility device.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My Heart Will Go On","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"The Heart Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"Information Broker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"Scales don't have arms!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"Penetration Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"Does this look infected?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"I See You've Handled Voids Before","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"The Mercyville Horror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003530/19fd774b2e523f4ea3f667b57c51490e62fd92df.jpg"},{"name":"I'm Over It","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.co